{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>有一个M行N列的点阵，相邻两点可以相连。一条纵向的连线花费一个单位，一条横向的连线花费两个单位。某些点之间已经有连线了，试问至少还需要花费多少个单位才能使所有的点全部连通。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"连接格点 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>输出使得连通所有点还需要的最小花费。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>第一行输入两个正整数m和n。<p><p>以下若干行每行四个正整数$x\\_1,y\\_1,x\\_2,y\\_2$，表示第$x\\_1$行第$y\\_1$列的点和第$x\\_2$行第$y\\_2$列的点已经有连线。输入保证$|x\\_1-x\\_2|+|y\\_1-y\\_2|=1$。<p>","examples":"<input>2 2\n1 1 2 1\n</input><output>3\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"【数据规模】\n30%数据：n\\*m≤1000\n100%数据：m,n≤1000\n","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1394","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100},{"output":"9.out","input":"9.in","score":100},{"output":"10.out","input":"10.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}